Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Equal Rights hold-up
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b0407byf
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 6 Mar 1977
Constitutional amendment to give Equal Rights to both sexes held up by states legislatures. The sound quality on this recording is variable/poor and the audio recording is incomplete. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less